---
// About section – Luiza is also a mentor
---
<section id="sobre" class="py-20 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
    <!-- Image -->
    <div class="relative reveal">
      <div class="rounded-[60px] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl aspect-square relative z-10">
        <img
          src="https://i.ibb.co/jvpdnB4m/487843042-2450645545322648-6455522586577811998-n.jpg"
          alt="Luiza Klassmann - Massoterapeuta e Mentora em Porto Alegre"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-sage/10 rounded-full -z-10 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-48 h-48 bg-brand-terracotta/10 rounded-full -z-10 blur-2xl"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Text -->
    <div class="reveal">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-10 leading-tight">
        Uma trajetória dedicada à <span class="text-brand-terracotta italic font-light">excelência</span> no toque.
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-8 text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed font-light text-lg">
        <p>
          Com anos de experiência e uma formação sólida, Luiza Klassmann consolidou-se como uma das principais referências em massoterapia de alta performance. Sua abordagem une técnica científica e sensibilidade, focando não apenas no alívio de sintomas, mas na recuperação funcional e estética do corpo.
        </p>
        <p>
          Além de seus atendimentos clínicos, Luiza atua como <strong class="text-brand-ink font-semibold">mentora de profissionais da área</strong>, capacitando novos talentos através de seus cursos presenciais e mentorias VIP, onde compartilha sua metodologia exclusiva de Liberação Miofascial.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-10 pt-8">
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-terracotta/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-brand-terracotta">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M15.477 12.89 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Autoridade</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-ink/50">Referência no ensino de terapias manuais.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-sage/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-brand-sage">
              <!-- Mentor/star icon -->
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3Z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="19" y2="22"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Mentora</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-ink/50">Formando profissionais de excelência.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-brand-gold">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Performance</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-ink/50">Foco em resultados reais e duradouros.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-terracotta/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-brand-terracotta">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Cuidado</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-brand-ink/50">Atendimento humanizado e personalizado.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
</style>
<script>
  const reveals = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) entry.target.classList.add('visible');
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.15 });
  reveals.forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
</script>
